2
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,640
(Directed by Liu Xue Song)

3
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:37,159
(Episode 34)

4
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,280
He did so many bad things.

5
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:54,319
Are you forgiving him just like that?

6
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,799
Zhirong Construction is where it is today...

7
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:01,840
thanks to his contributions.

8
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:05,079
But I never knew what he was thinking...

9
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,159
nor did I want to know.

10
00:02:08,810 --> 00:02:09,960
Even you, my son,

11
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:12,479
couldn't stand me after only a few months.

12
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:16,560
He stayed by my side for over a decade.

13
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:20,599
If I hadn't done wrong in the past,

14
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:23,599
he wouldn't have done wrong today.

15
00:02:24,090 --> 00:02:25,680
It happened because of me.

16
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,879
It's my burden to bear.

17
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:31,120
If I don't forgive him,

18
00:02:32,810 --> 00:02:34,840
the one who shouldn't be forgiven...

19
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:37,090
is me.

20
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:43,680
Mr. Hou, should I send you home?

21
00:02:43,810 --> 00:02:45,000
Let's go to the office.

22
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,360
Go home.

23
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,840
Dad, you must be tired.

24
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:52,919
No, I'm going to work.

25
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:05,879
Hello, Mr. Zhao. It's me, Hou Zhi Rong.

26
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:09,039
Liu Tie Hao will be discharged soon.

27
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:10,879
We need to increase the security for Hou Jue...

28
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,000
as soon as possible.

29
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,039
Okay.

30
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,400
I suddenly feel like my dad is getting old.

31
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,840
When he said he had forgiven Ma Yong,

32
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,360
I was really surprised.

33
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:28,960
He's nothing like the man I knew.

34
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,159
I feel the same way.

35
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,360
I used to think that...

36
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:40,039
he didn't understand me.

37
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,439
But I realized I don't understand him either.

38
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,400
I don't even know him.

39
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,319
Don't you want to go back and stay by his side?

40
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:54,479
He doesn't have anyone he could trust now.

41
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,240
No, I'm not going back.

42
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,159
Now is not the time.

43
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:02,439
Once I'm capable...

44
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,759
and strong,

45
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,639
then I can go back...

46
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,680
and help him out.

47
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,960
There's no point in going back now.

48
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:50,639
Hello, the number you dialed is turned off.

49
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:04,920
Is this Zhirong Construction? I'm looking for Ma Yong.

50
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:07,879
What?

51
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:43,720
Excuse me.

52
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:45,160
What did you just say?

53
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,519
Give me the room key.

54
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,800
Where is yours?

55
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,360
- Hurry up. - What are you doing?

56
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,959
I'm taking something home.

57
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:53,160
Take...

58
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:54,360
I'm sorry.

59
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:56,560
What are you taking? Where are you going?

60
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:58,399
Where are you going?

61
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,560
They caught Ma Yong.

62
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,160
What happened before,

63
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,399
including misappropriation of funds...

64
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:08,839
and proposal theft, was done by him.

65
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:10,000
He admitted it himself.

66
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,480
It's a huge blow to my dad.

67
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:15,319
He was betrayed by someone he trusted the most.

68
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:17,120
In my dad's language,

69
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:20,399
it's worse than having 100 more enemies by his side.

70
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,120
Get back to work.

71
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,199
I'll pack up and leave.

72
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:29,839
Monkey.

73
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:37,399
Enjoy.

74
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:49,399
Mr. Song.

75
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:52,879
Hey, buddy. I heard you got out.

76
00:08:53,210 --> 00:08:54,559
Yes, I'm out.

77
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:57,120
Before I get to visit you,

78
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,879
- you are already out. - It's okay.

79
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:02,000
It's good. Is everything okay?

80
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:03,559
Everything is good, Mr. Song.

81
00:09:04,090 --> 00:09:05,399
You're busy,

82
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,679
but you never forget your buddies.

83
00:09:07,210 --> 00:09:08,279
Everything is fine.

84
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,840
I just got out.

85
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,919
All my buddies know that.

86
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:12,159
They came to me and gave me money.

87
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,039
I can't stop them.

88
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:17,330
You're well-received.

89
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:19,399
Buddy.

90
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,330
What about the money you owe me?

91
00:09:21,330 --> 00:09:23,279
Including interest, it's 15,000 yuan now.

92
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:25,679
Since you are my buddy,

93
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:28,120
I haven't come to you.

94
00:09:28,450 --> 00:09:30,210
I won't charge you interest.

95
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:31,720
But as you know,

96
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,600
I have a lot of men now.

97
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:35,879
I don't make enough money to feed all of them.

98
00:09:36,090 --> 00:09:37,120
How about this?

99
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:39,360
I'll give you three days.

100
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,919
If you don't pay up,

101
00:09:40,919 --> 00:09:42,399
my men are on their way to find you.

102
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,720
I can't stop them, can I?

103
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,360
Please don't, Mr. Song.

104
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,799
Your men are so busy.

105
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,960
There's no time for me, right?

106
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:51,519
Since we are buddies,

107
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,120
give me one more week.

108
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,919
I'll raise more money.

109
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:56,519
I'll pay you back with interest.

110
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:58,799
I can even treat you and your men to a meal.

111
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,840
All right, three days.

112
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,960
No, Mr. Song.

113
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:05,000
You know I'm not good at anything except...

114
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,210
I'm not done yet.

115
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,360
No manners.

116
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,450
Boss, do you have a cigarette?

117
00:10:29,450 --> 00:10:30,759
No, you can get it outside.

118
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,330
But I've done...

119
00:10:35,330 --> 00:10:37,039
quite a number of huge projects.

120
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,679
I've done a lot of research too.

121
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:42,330
I think designers...

122
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:45,679
are in a way...

123
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:47,600
more like artists.

124
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,879
What we design...

125
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:52,799
- has to... - What a good life you have.

126
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:54,559
show others...

127
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:56,440
why we designed it.

128
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,480
It has to portray the personality of the designer.

129
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:00,960
That's why we have to make it fun.

130
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:03,639
Include some of your ideas...

131
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:05,879
- Hello. - and preferences.

132
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:07,279
Remember what you said today.

133
00:11:07,279 --> 00:11:08,480
Make it hard to tell,

134
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,679
but make others feel...

135
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:10,960
something different at the same time.

136
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,039
- What are you looking at? - The design industry...

137
00:11:12,039 --> 00:11:13,799
doesn't need the same thing over and over again.

138
00:11:13,799 --> 00:11:15,440
We don't want the same design...

139
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,639
from 100 designers.

140
00:11:16,759 --> 00:11:17,919
That's what we don't want to see.

141
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:20,480
They would rather buy...

142
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,159
- You haven't paid yet. - or live...

143
00:11:22,159 --> 00:11:24,960
in the high-quality houses that we designed.

144
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,519
- How much is it? - Twenty-five yuan.

145
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:28,799
I believe, through our design,

146
00:11:29,039 --> 00:11:31,799
the contractors...

147
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:34,480
- Keep the change. - will have better sales.

148
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,159
I also believe that from now on...

149
00:11:37,559 --> 00:11:38,720
Zhou Quan.

150
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,480
Hello, Hou Jue.

151
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:42,320
Nice to see you again.

152
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,519
You...

153
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:45,919
From today onwards,

154
00:11:45,919 --> 00:11:47,879
I'll take care of your security.

155
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:52,000
My dad hired you.

156
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:55,720
Liu Tie Hao has already finished serving his sentence.

157
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,159
He is out now.

158
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,279
Then how did you know I was here?

159
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,039
I...

160
00:12:04,879 --> 00:12:06,039
Tell me now.

161
00:12:06,039 --> 00:12:07,200
Don't you want to be friends?

162
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,600
Okay. It's no big deal.

163
00:12:11,279 --> 00:12:13,600
Actually, I've been here all along.

164
00:12:14,639 --> 00:12:16,200
You have been here all along? What do you mean?

165
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,799
I have been here from the moment you left home.

166
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,440
I even followed you to Shenzhen.

167
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,960
Why did I...

168
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,000
I didn't know.

169
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,080
I didn't even notice.

170
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,440
If you had noticed me,

171
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,440
I might as well quit.

172
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,480
All right.

173
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,200
I'll stay here for the next two days.

174
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,200
You know that, right?

175
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,600
You have to suffer for a while.

176
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,919
Come inside with me. Let's go.

177
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,120
No problem.

178
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,200
You have to change these parts in your report.

179
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,240
Is that so?

180
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,320
- Hello. - You're here.

181
00:13:00,519 --> 00:13:02,039
Superman, print the plan out.

182
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,320
All right.

183
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,519
- Mr. Bao. - Hello.

184
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:07,840
Hello, Mr. Bao.

185
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,159
Good news.

186
00:13:14,399 --> 00:13:15,480
Great King Company...

187
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:17,120
is very interested in our design.

188
00:13:17,799 --> 00:13:19,639
Brush up on your writing.

189
00:13:19,639 --> 00:13:20,639
Then we can print it.

190
00:13:23,159 --> 00:13:24,240
That's great.

191
00:13:25,279 --> 00:13:28,679
This time, I heard your dad...

192
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:32,120
designed the plan by himself.

193
00:13:34,559 --> 00:13:35,639
Do you know how many years it has been...

194
00:13:35,639 --> 00:13:37,320
since my dad did it himself?

195
00:13:37,519 --> 00:13:39,840
What happened this time?

196
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:42,960
I'm not sure.

197
00:13:43,399 --> 00:13:45,559
I only know that Zhirong Construction...

198
00:13:45,559 --> 00:13:46,639
is a mess inside.

199
00:13:46,639 --> 00:13:48,320
The elite troops have left.

200
00:13:52,519 --> 00:13:53,519
Hou Jue.

201
00:13:53,759 --> 00:13:55,399
Please pardon me.

202
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,240
If our design...

203
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,879
defeats your dad's,

204
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:04,519
would you feel...

205
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,679
We're here every day...

206
00:14:06,679 --> 00:14:08,840
working hard on the design day and night.

207
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,039
We fought and worked hard.

208
00:14:10,039 --> 00:14:11,240
What do you think is my aim?

209
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,840
I've been waiting for this day.

210
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:15,879
This time, if I don't defeat my dad,

211
00:14:16,919 --> 00:14:18,279
I would...

212
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,080
You know?

213
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:22,559
Okay, now I'm relieved.

214
00:14:22,759 --> 00:14:23,759
Carry on.

215
00:14:38,559 --> 00:14:39,559
Mr. Liu.

216
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,879
That jerk quit his dad's company.

217
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,240
Is he still worth anything?

218
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,000
Of course.

219
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:46,879
I was merely trying to scare him last time,

220
00:14:46,879 --> 00:14:48,080
his dad was terrified.

221
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,879
He gave me his money.

222
00:14:51,679 --> 00:14:52,799
Mr. Liu.

223
00:14:52,919 --> 00:14:55,960
What is our strategy this time?

224
00:14:56,879 --> 00:14:58,279
You guys hang out with me all the time.

225
00:14:58,279 --> 00:14:59,639
It seems that we hang out for nothing.

226
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,639
That lad designed a book bar.

227
00:15:05,679 --> 00:15:08,679
There is one at the South Bay Hotel.

228
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:11,279
Tomorrow is the hotel opening.

229
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,120
That lad must be here.

230
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,519
Got it?

231
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,399
If we go there on the opening day,

232
00:15:16,519 --> 00:15:18,720
the place will be crowded. It won't be easy.

233
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,879
Are you stupid?

234
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,759
It's easier to do it when the place is crowded.

235
00:15:22,759 --> 00:15:24,240
When it is crowded, people tend to get distracted.

236
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,320
No one will care about us.

237
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:26,960
Okay, got it.

238
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,399
Eat up.

239
00:15:28,919 --> 00:15:31,279
After this, we'll go for a walk and check out the spot.

240
00:15:39,559 --> 00:15:42,240
What do you mean? Why are you sighing so heavily?

241
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:45,559
I see.

242
00:15:46,279 --> 00:15:48,480
I take care of things well, okay?

243
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,200
If it is a success,

244
00:15:50,679 --> 00:15:52,679
everyone gets 10 percent.

245
00:15:53,399 --> 00:15:54,600
- Okay? - Okay.

246
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,440
